overview:
BizWayz is the first professional networking tool that bridges the gaps between the social networks to significantly expand your reach to people in business.

Your connections on the Social Networking sites are like separated islands with limited connections overlap - so you end up missing out on a great deal of mutual connections with people you wish to communicate with.

Using our patent pending “Discovery Engine”, we bridge the gaps between the Social Networks to help you uncover valuable “Hidden” connections you never knew you had.

BizWayz networking tool provides incredible value to Recruiters, Job Seekers, Sales Executives, Business Developers, Marketing Personnel and all other Professionals who seek to expand their engagement with the business community.
